      <div type="commentary" xml:lang="eng">
	<p>This edition and translation is based on <ref target="bibl:MNOVH2014">Nakanishi and von Hinüber 2014</ref>. Because it is on a cornice element, and because the upper pradakṣiṇapatha was only added in Phase III of the stūpa’s construction around 120 CE according to an inscription (<ref target="in:KanA8">KanA8</ref>), this inscription probably dates to around that time.</p>
      </div>
