      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
	<ab>The gift, a puphagahani and a slab showing) a Caitya (?), by the jeweller <persName key="pers:Kan-Mahāmariti">Mahāmariti(n)</persName> with his wife, with his son(s), with his daughter(s), with his son(s)-in-law.</ab>
